'''Mahendra Multiple Campus, Dharan''' (more colloquially : '''M. M. Campus''', {{lang-ne|महेन्द्र बहुमुखी क्याम्पस}}) is a public co-educational institution located in the Central part of the [[Dharan, Nepal|Dharan]] city and is one of the largest campuses affiliated to the [[Tribhuvan University]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Tribhuvan University Planning Division|title=Affiliated Campuses/Colleges under Tribhuvan University: FY 2067/68|url=http://www.tribhuvan-university.edu.np/downloads/Affiliated.pdf|publisher=Tribhuvan University|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724000419/http://tribhuvan-university.edu.np/downloads/Affiliated.pdf|archivedate=2013-07-24|df=}}</ref> The institution offers undergraduate and graduate (masters) programs. IIt is named after the king [[King Mahendra]]
